<style>
  .eva-size-guide {
    margin: 1.2rem 0;
  }
  .eva-size-guide__trigger {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .eva-size-guide__trigger svg {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .eva-size-guide__modal {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 9999;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 1.6rem;
  }
  .eva-size-guide__modal.is-open {
    display: flex;
  }
  .eva-size-guide__box {
    background: var(--color-background);
    border-radius: 0.4rem;
    max-width: 56rem;
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 90vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 3.2rem 2.4rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .eva-size-guide__close {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.2rem;
    right: 1.2rem;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0.4rem;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
  }
  .eva-size-guide__close svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
  }
  .eva-size-guide__title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 1.6rem;
  }
  .eva-size-guide__subtitle {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--color-foreground-secondary, #666);
    margin: 0 0 1.2rem;
  }
  .eva-size-guide table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  .eva-size-guide th {
    background: var(--color-base-accent-1, #f5f5f5);
    padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border, #e8e8e8);
  }
  .eva-size-guide td {
    padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border, #e8e8e8);
  }
  .eva-size-guide tr:nth-child(even) td {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
  }
  .eva-size-guide__tip {
    margin-top: 1.6rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-foreground);
    border-radius: 0 0.2rem 0.2rem 0;
  }
</style>

<div class="eva-size-guide">
  <button class="eva-size-guide__trigger" type="button" onclick="document.getElementById('eva-size-modal').classList.add('is-open')">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v17.25m0 0c-1.472 0-2.882.265-4.185.75M12 20.25c1.472 0 2.882.265 4.185.75M18.75 4.97A48.416 48.416 0 0 0 12 4.5c-2.291 0-4.545.16-6.75.47m13.5 0c1.01.143 2.01.317 3 .52m-3-.52 2.62 4.608a3 3 0 0 1-.379 3.408l-1.447 1.674a3 3 0 0 1-4.528 0l-1.447-1.674a3 3 0 0 1-.379-3.408L10.12 5.49m-6.37-.521 2.62 4.608a3 3 0 0 0 .379 3.408l1.447 1.674a3 3 0 0 0 4.528 0l1.447-1.674a3 3 0 0 0 .379-3.408L10.12 5.49" />
    </svg>
    Guia de tamanhos
  </button>
</div>

<div id="eva-size-modal" class="eva-size-guide__modal" onclick="if(event.target===this)this.classList.remove('is-open')">
  <div class="eva-size-guide__box">
    <button class="eva-size-guide__close" type="button" onclick="document.getElementById('eva-size-modal').classList.remove('is-open')" aria-label="Fechar">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18 18 6M6 6l12 12" />
      </svg>
    </button>
    <h2 class="eva-size-guide__title">Guia de Tamanhos — Calçados Femininos</h2>
    <p class="eva-size-guide__subtitle">Medindo seu pé: apoie o calcanhar numa parede e meça até a ponta do maior dedo.</p>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Número BR</th>
          <th>Comprimento do pé (cm)</th>
          <th>EUR</th>
          <th>USA</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>33</td><td>21,5 – 22,0</td><td>34</td><td>4</td></tr>
        <tr><td>34</td><td>22,0 – 22,5</td><td>35</td><td>4,5</td></tr>
        <tr><td>35</td><td>22,5 – 23,0</td><td>36</td><td>5</td></tr>
        <tr><td>36</td><td>23,0 – 23,5</td><td>37</td><td>5,5</td></tr>
        <tr><td>37</td><td>23,5 – 24,0</td><td>38</td><td>6</td></tr>
        <tr><td>38</td><td>24,0 – 24,5</td><td>38,5</td><td>6,5</td></tr>
        <tr><td>39</td><td>24,5 – 25,0</td><td>39</td><td>7</td></tr>
        <tr><td>40</td><td>25,0 – 25,5</td><td>40</td><td>7,5</td></tr>
        <tr><td>41</td><td>25,5 – 26,0</td><td>41</td><td>8</td></tr>
        <tr><td>42</td><td>26,0 – 26,5</td><td>42</td><td>8,5</td></tr>
        <tr><td>43</td><td>26,5 – 27,0</td><td>43</td><td>9</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p class="eva-size-guide__tip">
      💡 <strong>Dica:</strong> Se seu pé estiver entre dois tamanhos, escolha o maior. Para sandálias abertas, você pode escolher o menor.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
